Author: Aleph0-4
Text: It IS your ED brain and if you want to feel better about eating that amount, you have to keep doing it everyday until it becomes normal.

Author: half-bad
Text: Relatable. I ate a 700kcal meal yesterday and feel guilty, bloated, and all around disgusting today. Definitely going to need to restrict hard today and tomorrow to even begin to feel better about it :/
